citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:10am on October
24, 2023. The inspector spoke to an employee at the licensee's place of work who stated that the licensee was working
on a job away from the facility.
End Section
